citeinfo.title: Marbled Murrelet Nest Locations 1991-94

descript.abstract: Data Type: Birds; Marbled murrelet nest locations. 11 on Naked Island (1991, 1992, 1994). 1 Northwestern Lagoon, Kenai Fjords National Park (1993). 6 Port Nellie Juan (1994). The filenames and descriptions are as follows: 1) NESTHAB General habitat charastics of nest sites (1991) 2) NESTTREE Measurements of nest tree, branch, and nest (1991) 3) NTREES Measurements of all trees within 25m of nest tree (1991) 4) INLAND92 Nests found in 1992 5) NEST Nest charastics, measurements (1992) 6) NESTTREE Nest tree characteristics and measurements (1992) 7) NESTGEN Lat/long of nest, site characteristics (1992) 8) NTENTR92 Measurements of all trees within 25 meters of nest (1992)
